---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Growth Map | Business Clarity System for Founders"
  description="I help founders replace chaos with clarity. Get unstuck, focus your business, and grow without burning out."
  canonicalPath="/"
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-white px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-[1200px] flex-col items-center gap-12 md:flex-row md:gap-16">
      <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left">
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-bright-blue">
          Grow Revenue without the chaos
        </p>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold leading-tight text-navy sm:text-4xl md:text-[56px] md:leading-[1.1]">
          Running Your Business Shouldn't Feel This Hard
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-mid-gray md:text-xl">
          I help founders get unstuck, focus their business, and grow without burning out.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://calendar.notion.so/meet/cameronearloliver/qc3y04oud"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-lg bg-bright-blue px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:bg-[#0088c2]"
        >
          Book a Free Consult
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-shrink-0">
        <img
          src="/images/headshot.jpeg"
          alt="Cameron Oliver, founder of Growth Map"
          class="w-72 rounded-2xl shadow-lg md:w-80"
          loading="eager"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PAIN POINTS -->
  <section class="bg-light-gray px-6 py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy md:text-[40px] md:leading-tight">
        Does This Feel Familiar?
      </h2>
      <ul class="mt-10 space-y-5 text-left">
        {[
          "You've hit a ceiling you can't push through by working harder.",
          "You're tired of guessing what's actually going to move revenue.",
          "You're the default problem-solver for everything, and it's unsustainable.",
          "Your team is busy, but the results don't match the effort.",
          "You're carrying the weight of the business, and it's starting to bleed into the rest of your life.",
        ].map((item) => (
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-dark-text">
            <span class="mt-1.5 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-bright-blue" />
            {item}
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
      <a
        href="https://calendar.notion.so/meet/cameronearloliver/qc3y04oud"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="mt-10 inline-block rounded-lg bg-bright-blue px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:bg-[#0088c2]"
      >
        Book a Free Consult
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DESIRED STATE -->
  <section class="bg-white px-6 py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy md:text-[40px] md:leading-tight">
        What You Want Instead
      </h2>
      <ul class="mt-10 space-y-5 text-left">
        {[
          "To know exactly why the business is growing and how to keep it moving.",
          "To make decisions with clarity instead of instinct.",
          "A team that owns outcomes instead of handing you problems.",
          "Weeks that feel calm, predictable, and aligned.",
          "Growth that compounds without burning you out.",
        ].map((item) => (
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-dark-text">
            <span class="mt-1.5 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-bright-blue" />
            {item}
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
      <a
        href="https://calendar.notion.so/meet/cameronearloliver/qc3y04oud"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="mt-10 inline-block rounded-lg bg-bright-blue px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:bg-[#0088c2]"
      >
        Book a Free Consult
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STORY -->
  <section class="bg-light-gray px-6 py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
      <p class="mb-4 text-center text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-bright-blue">
        a better way to grow
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold text-navy md:text-[40px] md:leading-tight">
        The Story Behind Growth Map
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-dark-text">
        <p>
          Running a business is always hard — but there's a difference between productive hard and chaotic hard. I built Growth Map after watching founders struggle with wasted effort, misaligned hires, and unclear plans to win.
        </p>
        <p>
          When you understand how your business creates value, who delivers it, how to measure it, and what growth levers to pull, you can systematically scale your business.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <a
          href="/about"
          class="text-base font-semibold text-bright-blue transition-colors hover:text-navy"
        >
          Read More &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <section class="bg-white px-6 py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1200px]">
      <p class="mb-4 text-center text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-bright-blue">
        What We Offer
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold text-navy md:text-[40px] md:leading-tight">
        How We Can Work Together
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-light-gray p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy">Growth Map Diagnostic</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-dark-text">
            A fast, 30–60 minute clarity session that reveals how your business creates value, where growth is stuck, and the top levers that will move the business forward.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-mid-gray">
            Most founders don't have a growth problem — they have a clarity problem that makes growth impossible. The diagnostic exposes the levers that will move your revenue forward.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-light-gray p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy">The Growth Map Build</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-dark-text">
            A 90-day engagement where we map value engines, assign ownership, create your scorecard, and install a weekly cadence that replaces chaos with clarity.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-mid-gray">
            By the end of 90 days, your business will grow faster because your execution is cleaner, your decisions are sharper, and your team is aligned around what actually moves revenue.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-light-gray p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy">Fractional COO</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-dark-text">
            Hands-on execution support to run the operating model, drive improvements, and ensure your team stays aligned every week.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-mid-gray">
            My job isn't to keep the system running or to be a new manager; it's to continuously improve it so your business keeps growing without burning you out.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
